<div class="heads blue">
    <h2>Types of betting</h2>
</div>

<div class="callout">

    <p>There are the following types of betting in this organization:</p>

    <ul>
        <li><b>Single</b> - a classic one-event deal;</li>
        <li><b>Express</b> - up to 50 events (at other operators usually up to 20) odds of which are multiplied, the passage only in case of all correct predictions;
        </li>
        <li><b>Anti-Maggie</b> - the reverse type of Express, for passing it is necessary that at least 1 prediction turned out to be incorrect;
        </li>
        <li><b>System</b> - it is taken not by 1 Multi-fair, but by some smaller ones, due to it the return is possible even in case of one or more wrong predictions;
        </li>
        <li><b>Lucky</b> - a combination of singles and single bets, such combination also allows to receive at least a part of the profit in case of incorrect forecasts;</li>
        <li><b>series</b> - singles, which follow each other, after the winning of the first bet the whole sum of the winnings are put on the second and so on;
        </li>
        <li><b>Patent</b> - all possible combinations of singles and expresses from the selected number of events;
        </li>
        <li><b>Multibet</b> - the lobby is chosen; if it does not pass, the whole system loses; if it does pass, the odds of the system of other events are multiplied by the odds of the lobby;
        </li>
        <li><b>conditional betting</b> - as well as in a chain, outcome of the following bets depends on the previous ones, it is possible to bet in advance;
        </li>
        <li><b>live</b> - betting on the matches that are taking place right now.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <p>It is possible to choose the necessary type of betting in the betting slip. Before that, you need to form it. For that click on the odds of the events.</p>
</div>


